    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;evocation&nbsp;[force, light];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;cleric/oracle 3, paladin 3;\n    \n    <strong>Subdomain</strong>&nbsp;Hatred 2;\n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, DF<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;creature touched or all creatures within 5 ft.; see text<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute/level<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates (harmless);&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>A shimmering mantle of light shrouds the subject, light like a torch. The subject of the spell gains a +1 resistance bonus on all saving throws per four caster levels (maximum +5 at 20th level). The subject can end the <i>wrathful mantle</i> at any time as a swift action to deal 2d8 points of force damage to all creatures within 5 feet.</p>\n</div>\n",
